{"lastModified":1775132975736,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe Bali 5.4 Open Space redefines luxury with its enormous, flush-decked saloon, offering direct access to both the aft and forward cockpits. More importantly this boat has a good power-to-weight ratio, a well-designed hull shape, and robust center of gravity which ensures superior performance without compromising the comfort. Whether you’re relaxing in the spacious saloon, lounging in the forward cockpit, or enjoying panoramic views from the flybridge, the Bali 5.4 provides an unparalleled yachting experience.\n\nElegant and spacious, Namaste of Bali, flows openly forward and aft from the characteristic grand open salon. Experience maximum relaxation and fabulous service as your world class crew guides you on your Adriatic adventure.\n\nThe name \"Namaste of Bali\" combines the respectful greeting \"Namaste,\" symbolizing peace and connection, with \"Bali,\" the brand name of the catamaran, tropical paradise known for its beauty and tranquility. Together, it evokes a sense of serene luxury, harmony, and the exotic charm of Bali, offering an inviting and peaceful escape on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"NAMASTE OF BALI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::56956270-fdc5-11ef-9a8d-11b17498ce43/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5692f170-fdc5-11ef-ab5c-d96d510e7e36/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::56975e40-fdc5-11ef-9a8d-11b17498ce43/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::569a9290-fdc5-11ef-adcf-dfc7c97113ea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::56995a10-fdc5-11ef-adcf-dfc7c97113ea/{imageVariant}","/media/media